    "en": {
      "title": "The Committee on Parliamentary Affairs will meet tomorrow",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "A special meeting of the Committee on Parliamentary Affairs is scheduled to be held tomorrow (11th) at 2.00 pm. There, several matters are to be discussed, including the urgent assembly of the parliament and the decisions taken by the parliament in the current crisis situations.",
        "Last week, the Parliament met on the 4th, 5th and 6th, and at the end of the 6th Parliament, the Parliament was adjourned until the 19th at 10:00 am."
      ],
